    <item>
      <title>上诉法院解除美国禁令后苹果恢复手表销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/apple-watch-sales-ban-put-on-hold-by-appeals-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司(Apple Inc.)表示，在专利诉讼中赢得法院裁决后，周三将在其美国零售店重新销售最新款智能手表，为其170亿美元的业务提供快速喘息机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/apple-watch-sales-ban-put-on-hold-by-appeals-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:48:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《纽约时报》起诉微软和 OpenAI 侵犯版权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/new-york-times-sues-microsoft-and-openai-for-copyright-infringement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《纽约时报》起诉微软公司和 OpenAI 公司利用其内容帮助开发人工智能服务，这表明媒体与可能颠覆新闻行业的技术之间的关系日益紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/new-york-times-sues-microsoft-and-openai-for-copyright-infringement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 14:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
