      <title>MicroStrategy 最新购买的比特币持有量突破 80 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/microstrategy-mstr-bitcoin-holdings-top-8-billion-with-latest-purchase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业软件制造商 MicroStrategy Inc. 将购买比特币作为其企业战略的一部分，本月通过额外购买将其加密货币总持有量增加至超过 80 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/microstrategy-mstr-bitcoin-holdings-top-8-billion-with-latest-purchase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 14:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
